OL,6,     FPrisoners: The Tooting Popular
OL,7,     FFront, along with Mum and Dad, are
OL,8,     Fin for a long night when they get
OL,9,     Fheld up by fugitive Speed and his
OL,10,     Fgun-toting comrade MacTaggart.
OL,11,G0325 Citizen Smith
OL,12,     FCasablanca Was Never Like This:
OL,13,     FThe Tooting Popular Front hire a
OL,14,     Fprivate detective to prove Speed's
OL,15,     Finnocence - but haven't they met
OL,16,     Fthem somewhere before?
OL,17,G0400 Citizen Smith
OL,18,     FSweet Sorrow: Wolfie is determined
OL,19,     Fto save the Tooting he loves, but
OL,20,     Fthe stakes are high and he is soon
OL,21,     Fforced to go on the run.
